description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Anulomyces agalaxiae; Asterococcus agalactiae; Borrelomyces agalactiae; Capromyces agalactiae; Microbe de l'agalaxie contagieuse; Mycoplasmopsis agalactiae; Pleuropneumonia agalactiae.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
